description:
All Christians are now at war with Satan and his hosts. This is no time for weak knees or compromises with the powers of darkness. “Put on the whole armor of God,” urged Paul, “that you may be able to stand against the schemes of the devil.” Eph. 6:10. Watch Pastor Wohlberg explain Ephesians 6:10-18 and God’s call for us to stand strong for Jesus.
